License: GPL (>= 3)
Description: Fork of ggflags with additional flags added.
  A ggplot2 extension that allows you to plot the flags of the world. It functions essentially 
  as geom_point does, requiring, at minimum, a two-letter lowercase country code for the country aesthetic, 
  and x and y aesthetics. You can also adjust the size.
